description: Numbers that are the sum of 5 positive 5th powers.
links: T. D. Noe, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
mathematica: f[upto_]:=Module[{max=Floor[Power[upto, (5)^-1]],tp},tp=Union[ Total/@ (Tuples[ Range[max],{5}]^5)]; Select[tp,#<=upto&]]; f[2100]  (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Mar 22 2011 *)
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_
